# 1. Global Ignore Logic
**
!**/

# 2. Allow specific high-value file types
!**/*.md
!**/*.json
!**/*.yaml
!**/*.py
!**/*.sh
!**/*.txt
!**/RECOVERY*.md
!**/SESSION*.md
!.gitignore

# 3. EXCLUDE - High-churn transient directories (Dead Zones)
# These override the global allow rules above.
antigravity/code_tracker/**
antigravity/conversations/**
antigravity/implicit/**
antigravity/brain/**
history/**
antigravity-browser-profile/**
extensions/**
tmp/**
commands/**
**/__pycache__/**
*.pyc

# 4. Global Rule Files
!GEMINI.md
!GLOBAL_INDEX.md
!MISSION_NOMENCLATURE.md
!SELF_EVOLUTION_GLOBAL.md
!HOW_TO_USE_BEADS.md
!AGENT_ONBOARDING.md
!CROSS_COMPATIBILITY.md
!env.sh
